burlap.behavior.stochasticgames.madynamicprogramming

Class QSourceForSingleAgent.HashBackedQSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.stochasticgames.madynamicprogramming.QSourceForSingleAgent.HashBackedQSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QSourceForSingleAgent
    Enclosing interface:
    QSourceForSingleAgent

    public static class QSourceForSingleAgent.HashBackedQSource
extends Object
implements QSourceForSingleAgent
    An implementation of the QSourceForSingleAgent interface that has Q-values backed by hashmaps. Specifically, a map from hashed stats to a map from joint actions to stored JAQValue objects. This object also takes as QFunction object so that Q-values for state-joint-action pairs not previously stored can be initialized.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
